<author>frḥ ạlrbḍy</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - yạ mw̉mn kẖd slṭạnk rbk ʿlạlk sẖạnk
 rfʿk mʿh llsmwạt lạzm tʿrf mkạnk
 1- ylạ mạrs ạymạnk ạ̹sm yswʿ hw ḍmạnk
 whbk fy kl ạlbrkạt ( kl wʿwdh ʿlsẖạnk )2
 2- ḥạrb drʿk br yswʿ wklạmh fy qlbk mrfwʿ
 fy ạlrwḥ ạ̉skb ṣlạwạt ( ṣwtk ʿnd ạllh msmwʿ )2
 3- ylạ ạ̹lbs kl slạḥk nṣrk mḍmwn wnjạḥk
 lạ ttrk ạ̉bdạ tẖgẖrạt ( ḥty̱ tkml ạ̉frạḥk )2
 4- ạ̉ly fyk ạ̉qwy mnh ạlrb fyk wạnt ạ̹bnh
 qạwm wạ̹tqdm btẖbạt ( syf ạlrwḥ yhdm ḥṣnh )2
 5- ạlsẖyṭạn mgẖlwb mgẖlwb mn ywm mạ ạ̹rtfʿ ạlmṣlwb
 dm yswʿ ḥsm ạlṣrạʿạt ( nṣrk ṣạr nṣrk mḥswb )2</lyrics>
<title>yạ mw̉mn kẖd slṭạnk</title>
</song>